<p>Second, there's just <em>one</em> rule that we need to follow about roles: every user must have
at least <em>one</em> role. Otherwise, weird stuff happens.</p>
<p>That's no problem - just make sure that <em>everyone</em> at least has <code>ROLE_USER</code> by saying:
<code>if (!in_array('ROLE_USER', $roles))</code>, then add that to <code>$roles</code>. Finally, <code>return $roles</code>:</p>
