<h2 id="migration-amp-fixtures">Migration &amp; Fixtures <a class="headerlink" href="dynamic-roles#migration-amp-fixtures" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Generate the migration for the new field:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./bin/console doctrine:migrations:diff</div></code></pre>
<p>We should double-check that migration, but let's just run it:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate</div></code></pre>
<p>Finally, give some roles to our fixture users! For now, we'll give everyone the same
role: <code>ROLE_ADMIN</code>:</p>
